target_id: FIBO FND Domain, North American Extension
Financial Industry Business Ontology (FIBO) Foundations (FND) Domain, North American Extension

The North American extension of the Foundations (FND) domain builds on the more general FND ontologies with concepts that are specific to the North American region of the world, such as those defining North American addresses.
Office of Financial Research (US Dept of the Treasury)

The 'all' ontology for Foundations (FND), North American Extension is provided for convenience for FIBO users. This ontology does not add new assertions, but imports the Production (Released) ontologies that comprise the FIBO Foundations (FND) domain, including extensions related to postal addressing in the US and Canada.
